This script is designed for quick installation of essential tools that I regularly use on virtual machines and new systems.

Please note that this script has only been tested on 3 operating systems thus far, and further testing on other operating systems is required. It is important to emphasize that this is not the final version of the script.

The following tools are installed by this script:

cURL
wget
dig
wireshark
ssh
nmap
nc
vim
gdb with gef
nikto
hydra
sqlmap
john
impacket
crackmapexec
pwntools
masscan
pwncat
P.E.A.S.S.
SecLists
wpscan
ffuf
gobuster
amass
mimikatz
sublist3r
enum4linux
enum4linux-ng
ghidra
metasploit
exploitdb
